/target
**/*.rs.bk
Cargo.lock.bak
.DS_Store

# Python dev environment lives at the repo root (.venv/) per CLAUDE.md.
# Both the root and any accidental nested copies are excluded so a
# skill bundle stays a clean SKILL.md-shaped artifact.
.venv/
**/.venv/
__pycache__/
**/__pycache__/
.pytest_cache/
**/.pytest_cache/
*.egg-info/
**/*.egg-info/

# TypeScript / Node dev environment for the Obsidian plugin
# (and any future TS components). node_modules/ is per-project per
# the Obsidian convention — gitignored at every level so a stray
# `npm install` inside a sub-tree does not pollute the tree.
# The bundled `main.js` is a build artifact and lives next to the
# manifest in production installs, but stays out of git so the
# committed source is the source of truth.
node_modules/
**/node_modules/
obsidian-plugin/main.js
obsidian-plugin/main.js.map
